==Crowned frog==
* '''Frog:''' Please help me. I was transformed into a frog by a well-meaning but sadly frog-obsessed old wizard. Only your touch can turn me back. Will you help me?
* {{tact|One positive and one negative option are presented in a random order:}}
* {{topt|cond=Positive dialogue 1:|Okay.}}
** '''Player:''' Okay.
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|cond=Positive dialogue 2:|Alright.}}
** '''Player:''' Alright.
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|cond=Positive dialogue 3:|Sure, I will.}}
** '''Player:''' Sure, I will.
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|cond=Positive dialogue 4:|Yeah, okay.}}
** '''Player:''' Yeah, okay.
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|cond=Positive dialogue 5:|I suppose so, sure.}}
** '''Player:''' I suppose so, sure.
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|cond=Positive dialogue 6:|All right.}}
** '''Player:''' All right.
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|cond=Positive dialogue 7:|Very well, if a touch is all you need, I'll do it.}}
** '''Player:''' Very well, if a touch is all you need, I'll do it.
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|cond=Positive dialogue 8:|Yes, I will touch you.}}
** '''Player:''' Yes, I will touch you.
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|cond=Positive dialogue 9:|Sure, I'll touch you.}}
** '''Player:''' Sure, I'll touch you.
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|cond=Positive dialogue 10:|A touch? Yes, I'll do that.}}
** '''Player:''' A touch? Yes, I'll do that.
** {{tact|continue}}

* {{topt|cond=Negative-teleport dialogue 1:|No way, I'm not kissing you.}}
** '''Player:''' No way, I'm not kissing you.
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|cond=Negative-teleport dialogue 2:|I'd rather not.}}
** '''Player:''' I'd rather not.
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|cond=Negative-teleport dialogue 3:|Eww, no way!}}
** '''Player:''' Eww, no way!
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|cond=Negative-teleport dialogue 4:|I don't want to.}}
** '''Player:''' I don't want to.
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|cond=Negative-teleport dialogue 5:|Leave me alone.}}
** '''Player:''' Leave me alone.
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|cond=Negative-teleport dialogue 6:|A kiss? Not a chance.}}
** '''Player:''' A kiss? Not a chance.
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|cond=Negative-teleport dialogue 7:|It looks better to be a frog. Make me one!}}
** '''Player:''' It looks better to be a frog. Make me one!
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|cond=Negative-teleport dialogue 8:|I'd rather become a frog too!}}
** '''Player:''' I'd rather become a frog too!
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|cond=Negative-teleport dialogue 9:|What if I want to be a frog like you?}}
** '''Player:''' What if I want to be a frog like you?
** {{tact|continue}}

* {{topt|cond=Negative-polite dialogue 1:|I would prefer not to, sorry.}}
** '''Player:''' I would prefer not to, sorry.
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|cond=Negative-polite dialogue 2:|I'm sorry, I'd prefer not to do that.}}
** '''Player:''' I'm sorry, I'd prefer not to do that.
** {{tact|continue}}

* {{topt|cond=Kiss option 1:|How about if we kiss?}}
** '''Player:''' How about if we kiss?
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|cond=Kiss option 2:|May I kiss you instead?}}
** '''Player:''' May I kiss you instead?
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|cond=Kiss option 3:|Would a kiss be acceptable?}}
** '''Player:''' Would a kiss be acceptable?
** {{tact|continue}}

* {{tcond|If the positive option was chosen:}}
** '''Frog:''' Thank you so much, [player name]. I must return to my fairytale kingdom. But take this as a reward. You can exchange it at the Varrock clothes store for a costume.
** {{tact|receives=frog token}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the negative-teleport option was chosen:}}
** {{qact|Player is transformed into a frog and teleported to Frogland}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the negative-polite option was chosen:}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the kiss option was chosen:}}
** '''Frog:''' Yes!
** '''Frog [Prince/Princess]:''' Thank you so much, [player name]. I must return to my fairytale kingdom. But take this as a reward. You can exchange it at the Varrock clothes store for a costume.
** {{tact|receives=frog token}}
** {{tact|end}}

