==Overhead dialogue==
* {{tcond|Upon spawning in for the player:}}
** '''Frog:''' {{overhead|Greetings from the [prince/princess], [player name]!}}
* {{tcond|While waiting for a response by the player:}}
** {{trandom}}
** {{topt|Dialogue 1}}
*** '''Frog:''' {{overhead|Talk to the frog [prince/princess], [player name]!}}
** {{topt|Dialogue 2}}
*** '''Frog:''' {{overhead|The frog [prince/princess] needs your help, [player name]!}}
** {{topt|Dialogue 3}}
*** '''Frog:''' {{overhead|Please respond to the frog [prince/princess], [player name]!}}
* {{tcond|If the player does not respond in time:}}
** '''Frog:''' {{overhead|Maybe later.}}

==Frogland==
* '''Frog:''' Are you ready to leave now?
* {{topt|Yes, I'd like to leave now.}}
** '''Player:''' Yes, I'd like to leave now.
** {{qact|Player is transformed back and teleported to their initial spot}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|No, I'd rather stay.}}
** '''Player:''' No, I'd rather stay.
** {{tact|end}}
